com.stackmob.sdk.model
Class StackMobField

java.lang.Object
  com.stackmob.sdk.model.StackMobField

public class StackMobField
extends Object

Specifies constraints on a field for use in a query. This is meant to be used as part of StackMobModelQuery to simplify setting multiple constraints on the same field. 

 StackMobModelQuery<User> isThirtySomethingQuery2 = new StackMobModelQuery<User>(User.class).field(new StackMobField("age").isGreaterThanOrEqualTo(30).isLessThan(40))
